<br>
1 Magi -Darktwins- <br>
pull the starting cards and if your not against another DT you go first get 7 and use Dream Rift for another 3... now you&#39;ve gone though 10 or the 40 cards in your deck. hopefully your get a Secrets of the book hold one to it for your next turn when they have cards in there hand. then lay down Wudge and a lot of cards unless you know your opponent is Arderial and is going to hit you with a Catalsym. Or Xyx Elders hurt too. ... your focusing on giving Harror lots of cards. <br>
<br>
2 Magi -Harror- <br>
get your starting cards and if your opponent has more energy then 10-11 on there creatures use that Catalsym and kick there butt. <br>
<br>
<br>
Combo&#39;s to look for... <br>
Black Agovo+ Secrets of the book... use the book to see there hand and if they don&#39;t have anti-discard cards use your Black agovo to weaken there hand its best done when they only have 3 cards then the next turn they have nothing new to put down. <br>
<br>
watch for Dark Ayebaw it can win you the game just discarding the hoard of cards you should get after DT get a book. <br>
<br>
